description:
On a continent protected by four witches stands Winfred Academy, a prestigious school of magic. When an incident occurs at the school, Anz finds himself right in the middle of it&hellip;
[hr][b][u]French / Fran&ccedil;ais[/u][/b]
[spoiler]A l'Acad&eacute;mie Winfred, prestigieuse &eacute;cole de magie, les &eacute;l&egrave;ves n'ont qu'une chose en t&ecirc;te : devenir la prochaine sorci&egrave;re du vent, l'une des quatre sorci&egrave;res prot&eacute;geant le continent. Au milieu de cette effervescence, Anz essaye tant bien que mal d'&eacute;viter les ennuis...[/spoiler]

[from lost-translations]

&ldquo;I want a boyfriend!&rdquo;

Kozakura Nonoka always fancied having a boyfriend. Upon entering high school, she was certain that she was finally going to get one, but fast-forwarding eight months to December, she was still single as ever. Desperate, she attended a goukon (a group blind date) where she met Kiriyama Naoya, whose first words to her was &ldquo;You&rsquo;ll never get a boyfriend.&rdquo;

Now, what would this strange meet-up lead to?

A shriek was heard as a sailor uniform skirt fluttered, and Meguru thought himself a lucky perv until he caught a glimpse of... a guy's boxer shorts?

&quot;Quit staring, old fart!&quot;

By chance, he ended up inviting the high school boy in a girl's uniform, Keiichi, to his place, with the mystery of why he wears that uniform still unsolved. Unwittingly, however, Meguru discovered the reason behind Keiichi's uniform...
[hr][b][u]Polish / Polski:[/u][/b]
[spoiler]Dało się usłyszeć gromki krzyk, gdy zatrzepotała sp&oacute;dniczka od mundurka, a Meguru uznał, że m&oacute;głby być zboczuchem-szczęściarzem, aż do chwili, kiedy pod sp&oacute;dniczką zobaczył męskie bokserki.
&ldquo;Czego się gapisz, stary pierdzielu?!&rdquo;
Meguru w końcu zaprasza do siebie licealistę Keiichiego - chłopaka w damskim ciuchach. Pow&oacute;d dla kt&oacute;rego zakłada sp&oacute;dniczkę, wciąż pozostaje niewyjaśniony, jednak Meguru przez przypadek odkrywa tajemnicę stroju Keiichiego&hellip;
Dwa serca połączone ze sobą i opowieść o pierwszej miłości.
Wystarczy sięgnąć, by być bliżej twego serca.
